import{createSlice}from"@reduxjs/toolkit";import{v4 as uuidv4}from"uuid";export const UsersSlice=createSlice({name:"users",initialState:{value:[]},reducers:{addUser:(e,a)=>{a.payload&&(e.value="string"==typeof a.payload?[...e.value,{name:a.payload,id:uuidv4()}]:[...e.value,{name:a.payload.name,id:a.payload.id}])},editUser:(e,a)=>{e.value=e.value.map((e=>e.id===a.payload.id?{...e,name:a.payload.name}:e))},removeUser:(e,a)=>{e.value=e.value.filter((e=>e.id!==a.payload))}}});export const{addUser:addUser,editUser:editUser,removeUser:removeUser}=UsersSlice.actions;export const selectUsers=e=>e.users.value;export const selectUsersNumber=e=>e.users.value.length;export default UsersSlice.reducer;